{"lemma":"إِعاداتٌ","slug":"إِعاداتٌ","root":"ع.#.د","root_slug":"ع-_-د","root_link":"/words/roots/ع-_-د","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":2},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n30931"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%A5%D9%90%D8%B9%D8%A7%D8%AF%D8%A7%D8%AA%D9%8C"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of أَعَادَ (ʔaʕāda) (form IV)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"reconduction, repeat undertaking or restoration"}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n30931","headword_ar":"اعادهُ","root":"Ewd","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"(O, K)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He returned it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"restored it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K,)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_ilaY makaAnihi","text_ar":"اـِلَى مَكَانِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to its place; he replaced it"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (O, K.) ―         -b2-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He did it a second time:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he repeated it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"iterated it;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kar~arahu","text_ar":"كَرَّرَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; namely, speech; (K;) as also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lahu","text_ar":"لَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EaAda","text_ar":"عَادَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":";"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he said it a second time;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh;) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_ilayohi","text_ar":"اـِلَيْهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EAd","text_ar":"عاد","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ealayohi","text_ar":"عَلَيْهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[likewise] signify the same as"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AEAdhu","text_ar":"اعادهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (TA:) but Aboo-Hilál El-'Askeree says that"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kar~arahu","text_ar":"كَرَّرَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies he repeated it once or more than once; whereas"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AEAdhu","text_ar":"اعادهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies only"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he repeated it once:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(MF, TA:)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AEAd AlkalaAma","text_ar":"اعاد الكَلَامَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"mean"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he repeated the speech"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"saying it"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a second time;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rad~adahu vaAniyFA","text_ar":"رَدَّدَهُ ثَانِيًا"},{"kind":"text","text":". (O.) One says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AEAd AlS~alaApa","text_ar":"اعاد الصَّلَاةَ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He said the prayer a second time."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA yubodiy^u wamaA yuEiydu","text_ar":"مَا يُبْدِيُ وَمَا يُعِيدُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mA yatakal~amu bibaAdiy^apK walaA EaAy^idapK","text_ar":"ما يَتَكَلَّمُ بِبَادِيَةٍ وَلَا عَايِدَةٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Lth, A, O,) i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He does not say anything for the first time; nor anything for the second time;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"anything original, nor anything in the way of repetition;"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baAdiy^apu AlkalaAmi","text_ar":"بَادِيَةُ الكَلَامِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifying"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"what is said for the first time;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlkalaAmi","text_ar":"الكَلَامِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EaAy^idapu","text_ar":"عَايِدَةُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"what is said for the second time, afterwards:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bdA^","text_ar":"بدا"},{"kind":"text","text":":) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he says not anything:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A:) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he has no art, artifice,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"cunning."},{"kind":"text","text":"(IAar, TA; and A in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bdA^","text_ar":"بدا"},{"kind":"text","text":"; q. v.) ―         -b3-  [Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He returned it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"restored it, to a former state:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and hence,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he renewed it: he reproduced it."},{"kind":"text","text":"] One says of God,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yubodiy^u Alxaloqa","text_ar":"يُبْدِيُ الخَلْقَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vum~a yuEiyduhu","text_ar":"ثُمَّ يُعِيدُهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He createth,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"bringeth into existence, mankind:"},{"kind":"text","text":"] then"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He returneth them, after life, to lifelessness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"in the present world;"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and after lifelessness, to life,"},{"kind":"text","text":"on the day of resurrection. (TA.) ―         -b4-  See also 8. ―         -b5-  ["},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AEAd","text_ar":"اعاد"},{"kind":"text","text":"also signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it, rendered;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"made to be,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"become;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaEala","text_ar":"جَعَلَ"},{"kind":"text","text":";) in which sense it is doubly trans.: see an ex. in a verse cited voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EasiyfN","text_ar":"عَسِيفٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".]"}],"source_refs":["O","K","S","Msb","TA","MF","Lth","A"]}]}}